---

# Build Instructions

## Requirements

Install:

* Visual Studio 2022
* CMake
* IBM ILOG CPLEX Studio 22.1.2

---

# Configure CPLEX Path

In `CMakeLists.txt`:

```cmake
set(CPLEX_ROOT
    "C:/Program Files/IBM/ILOG/CPLEX_Studio_Community2212"
)
```

Adjust the path if your installation differs.

---

# Build

From the project root:

```powershell
cmake -B out/build
cmake --build out/build --config Release
```

---

# Run

```powershell
.\out\build\Release\yield_management.exe
```

---

# Example Output

```text
